c: 12
v: 41
t: "Casbit yô luk tan yi namma kataysaw: siinik numuk teynah tugactek usuk casbik awqeleeh isi amoyta gocoy afqele, akattuy gaqambo moyyal yakkuqem isik yubleh tugactek fannisimeleeh haada kay moyyak cado akmele, isin warsa kak faxxeeniih esserten caagid meklimeeh gaba kaleh keenik iyye Nabii Yuusuf"